dct_title_s: Riggen & Holbrook's map of Portland and environs
dct_description_sm: Shows additions, lot numbers, street names, and railroads; shows selected landowners.; "Entered according to act of Congress, in the year 1889 by W.H. Whitney in the Office of the Librarian of Congress at Washington."; "L.H. Everts engraver, Phila. Pa."; Map has public land (township, range, and section) grid.
